msgctxt "an8.119:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.119:0.2"
msgid "11. Rāgapeyyāla "
msgstr "11. Abbreviated Texts Beginning With Greed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.119:0.3"
msgid "119 "
msgstr "119 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.349, sc1
msgctxt "an8.119:1.1"
msgid "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya aṭṭha dhammā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "“For insight into greed, eight things should be developed. "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.3"
msgid "Ajjhattaṃ rūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati parittāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni, "
msgstr "Perceiving form internally, they see visions externally, limited, both pretty and ugly. "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.4"
msgid "tāni abhibhuyya ‘jānāmi passāmī’ti evaṃsaññī hoti. "
msgstr "Mastering them, they perceive: ‘I know and see.’ "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.5"
msgid "Ajjhattaṃ rūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati appamāṇāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni, tāni abhibhuyya ‘jānāmi passāmī’ti evaṃsaññī hoti. "
msgstr "Perceiving form internally, they see visions externally, limitless, both pretty and ugly. … "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.6"
msgid "Ajjhattaṃ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati parittāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni, tāni abhibhuyya ‘jānāmi passāmī’ti evaṃsaññī hoti. "
msgstr "Not perceiving form internally, they see visions externally, limited, both pretty and ugly. … "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.7"
msgid "Ajjhattaṃ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati appamāṇāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni, tāni abhibhuyya ‘jānāmi passāmī’ti evaṃsaññī hoti. "
msgstr "Not perceiving form internally, they see visions externally, limitless, both pretty and ugly. … "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.8"
msgid "Ajjhattaṃ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati nīlāni nīlavaṇṇāni nīlanidassanāni nīlanibhāsāni "
msgstr "Not perceiving form internally, they see visions externally, blue, with blue color, blue hue, and blue tint. … "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.9"
msgid "pītāni pītavaṇṇāni … pe … "
msgstr "yellow … "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.10"
msgid "lohitakāni lohitakavaṇṇāni … pe … "
msgstr "red … "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.11"
msgid "odātāni odātavaṇṇāni … pe … odātanibhāsāni, "
msgstr "Not perceiving form internally, they see visions externally, white, with white color, white hue, and white tint. "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.12"
msgid "tāni abhibhuyya ‘jānāmi passāmī’ti evaṃsaññī hoti—"
msgstr "Mastering them, they perceive: ‘I know and see.’ "

msgctxt "an8.119:1.13"
msgid "rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime aṭṭha dhammā bhāvetabbā”. "
msgstr "For insight into greed, these eight things should be developed.”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
